Write a Python program to enter sentence of atleast 10 words. Take user input of lengtho of word. 

Find the word in user inputed string which has >= length of word enter by user and creaet its directory where word is key and its length is value.

For Example : 

Enter String : My college name is Vidyabharti Trust college of Business Computer Science and Research. My College is located at Umrakh.

Minimum World length :  6

{"college":7, "Vidyabharti":11, "Business":8, "Computer":8,"Science":7,"Research":8,"Umrakh":1}
